== MONEY-RUN - Avik Das, Israel Jacques ===============================

A side-scrolling platformer with an emphasis on simplicity. The goal of
this game is as follows:

* Build an actual game instead of simply a tech demo.
* Be simple enough to finish within a week.
* Promote collaboration between two friends who have only worked on
  school projects together.
* Have fun developing an NES game.

~~ RUNNING ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

To assemble and run money-run using an emulator like FCEUX:

  make
  fceux money-run.nes

~~ FUNCTIONALITY ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This is a work-in-progress, so there is no functionality yet.
